				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-9">
					<div class="d-lg-flex post-entry-2">
						<div>
							<h3>
								Nos simulateurs sont gratuits, ils vous aideront à comparer.
							</h3>
							<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Distinctio placeat exercitationem magni voluptates dolore. Tenetur fugiat voluptates quas, nobis error deserunt aliquam temporibus sapiente, laudantium dolorum itaque libero eos deleniti?</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-lg-12">
							<div class="post-entry-1">
								<h3>Simulateur charbon / pétrole</h3>
								<canvas data-controller="chart" data-chart-data-value='{ "labels": ["January", "February", "March", "April", "May", "June", "July"], "datasets": [{ "label": "My First dataset", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "borderColor": "#3B82F6", "data": [37, 83, 78, 54, 12, 5, 99] }] }'></canvas>
								<div class="post-meta">
									<span class="date"></span>
								</div>
								<h2 class="mb-2">
									Un expert à votre écoute
								</h2>
								<span class="author mb-3 d-block">Si vous rencontrez une difficulté ou pour demander un conseil.</span>
								<form action="forms/contact.php" method="post" role="form" class="php-email-form">
									<div class="row">
										<div class="form-group col-md-6">
											<input type="text" name="name" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="Votre nom & prénom" required="">
										</div>
										<div class="form-group col-md-6">
											<input type="email" class="form-control" name="email" id="email" placeholder="Votre email" required="">
											<small id="helpId" class="form-text text-muted">Votre email ne sera pas communiqué à des tiers.</small>
										</div>
									</div>
									<div class="form-group mt-1">
										<textarea class="form-control" name="message" rows="3" placeholder="Votre question" required=""></textarea>
									</div>
									<div class="text-center mt-1">
										<button class="btn btn-primary ">Envoyer le message</button>
									</div>
								</form>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="col-md-3">
					<div class="post-entry-1 border-bottom">
						<h3 class=" mb-2 h5">
							<a href="single-post.html">Comparateur EDF/GDF</a>
						</h3>

						<span class="author mb-3 d-block">Ce comparateur vous permettra d'effectuer en quelques clics une simulation sur votre consommation.</span>
					</div>


				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
